OL,4,Ctraffic with no confirmed re-opening
OL,5,Cdate
OL,7,FAlbert Bridge has been closed to
OL,8,Ftraffic until further notice after
OL,9,Fsafety concerns were raised during
OL,10,Froutine maintenance.
OL,12,FThe council said teams were examining
OL,13,Fthe crossing between Chelsea and
OL,14,FBattersea, which remains open to
OL,15,Fpedestrians, but they needed to "take
OL,16,Ftime to understand what's happened".
OL,18,FThe bridge is over 150 years old, used
OL,19,Fby 20,000 cars each day, and serves as
OL,20,Fa key route for residents and
OL,21,Fbusinesses.
