OL,7,F"We don't know yet how long it will be
OL,8,Fclosed, but our teams were on site
OL,9,Flast week, they're on site again this
OL,10,Fweek," said Conservative Councillor
OL,11,FJohnny Thalassites, lead Member for
OL,12,FEnvironment and Planning at the Royal
OL,13,FBorough of Kensington and Chelsea
OL,14,FCouncil.
OL,16,F"We're going to find out as soon as
OL,17,Fpossible what's happened and how to
OL,18,Fget it back open.
