OL,7,F"I totally understand how disruptive
OL,8,Fit is for people that want to get
OL,9,Faround London.
OL,11,F"This is a 150-year-old bridge - it's
OL,12,Fan iconic Grade II-listed bridge.
OL,14,F"With old infrastructure across London
OL,15,Fsometimes you do find issues so I'm
OL,16,Fpleased that our routine maintenance
OL,17,Fpicked this up because we want to get
OL,18,Fto it as early as we can and make sure
OL,19,Fthat it's safe.
