OL,7,F"We already have a restriction on
OL,8,FAlbert Bridge to keep some of the
OL,9,Fheaviest vehicles off the surface to
OL,10,Ftry and prolong the bridge's life.
OL,12,F"And we're going to keep doing
OL,13,Feverything that we can, whether that's
OL,14,Freactive repairs here or proactive
OL,15,Fmaintenance in the future to try and
OL,16,Fkeep it open."
OL,18,FThe council will be keen to avoid a
OL,19,Frepeat of the long-term controversial
OL,20,Fclosure of Hammersmith Bridge which is
OL,21,Fonly open to pedestrians and cyclists.
