OL,7,FThe crossing over the River Thames in
OL,8,Fwest London has been closed to motor
OL,9,Fvehicles since April 2019 after a
OL,10,Fsafety assessment uncovered dangerous
OL,11,Fmicrofractures in the castiron
OL,12,Fpedestals.
OL,14,FThe fractures made the crossing unsafe
OL,15,Ffor cars, buses and heavy traffic.
OL,17,FCllr Thalassites added: "I certainly
OL,18,Fdon't want this to be another
OL,19,FHammersmith Bridge.
