OL,7,F"We've got a budget for repairs and
OL,8,Fmaintenance of our bridges in
OL,9,FKensington & Chelsea.
OL,11,F"So we're taking the steps that we
OL,12,Fneed to mitigate the risk of that and
OL,13,FI want to see this bridge open to
OL,14,Fpedestrians and vehicles as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible."
OL,17,FCompleted in 1873, the listed crossing
OL,18,Fis renowned for its pastel Victorian
OL,19,Fdesign and unique combination of
OL,20,Fsuspension and cable-stayed
OL,21,Fengineering.
