OL,7,FBeyond its practical role, it has
OL,8,Fbecome a beloved local landmark,
OL,9,Fvalued for its historic significance,
OL,10,Fscenic riverside setting, and place at
OL,11,Fthe heart of the community.
OL,13,FTimeline of London's Albert Bridge
OL,15,F1873 - OpeningJAlbert Bridge, designed
OL,16,Fby Rowland Mason Ordish and named
OL,17,Fafter Prince Albert, opens as a hybrid
OL,18,Fsuspension and cable-stayed bridge
OL,19,Flinking Chelsea and Battersea.
